request.description:
This allows you to update the user's (driver's & passenger's) cell number, gender (male, female) , dob (23-12-2020), profile picture & password.

If you only want to upload the profile picture, then you don't have to send the "attribute" & "value" as an argument. 

You can not upload the profile picture & edit an attribute in the same API call to the server. :)
